data.description: Do you like everything in a home to be new? New HVAC, new water heater, new flooring, new paint, new bathtub, new light fixtures, and new everything else? Well this is the home for you! This property features 4 beds, 2 baths, an open concept living and kitchen area, and a separate room that could be an office, formal dining, a playroom, and beyond! This homeowner spared nothing in getting this property ready for the market! Newly renovated bathrooms feature on trend colors and finishes! Nice sized lot features a great backyard! This home is a must see! Don't miss your shot! Call to book your private showing today! Check out the virtual tour!
